item.title: CVE-2020-2136|2024-08-04T07:01:40.826Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20git%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Git Plugin 4.2.0 and earlier does not escape the error message for the repository URL for Microsoft TFS field form validation, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting vulnerability.
